name: Great of Praises
description:
Nefertari has been dubbed the most mysterious queen. The name Nefertari means a beautiful woman has come. Not only did she have a laudatory name, but Nefertari also had other titles besides the great empress.

Some of her other titles are Hereditary Princess, Great of Praises, Lady of Grace, Sweet of Love, Lady of The Two Lands, Great King's Wife, her beloved, Lady of all Women, Mistress of Upper and Lower Egypt, Wife of the Strong Bull, and High Priestess of Athens. These titles represent his status and role in the reign of the ancient Egyptian era.
